<li>EPA pages: <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.epa.gov/criteria-air-pollutants">"Criteria Air Pollutants"</a>. April 9, 2014.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Criteria+Air+Pollutants&amp;rft.date=2014-04-09&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fcriteria-air-pollutants&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AClean+Air+Act+%28United+States%29" class="Z3988"></span> <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.epa.gov/naaqs">"NAAQS"</a>. September 9, 2016.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=NAAQS&amp;rft.date=2016-09-09&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fnaaqs&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AClean+Air+Act+%28United+States%29" class="Z3988"></span></li></ul>
